{"build_type":"library","description":"Parent-side: carve a per-thread worker arena SEED block (g_worker_arena_bytes, default 4 MiB) from the pool via grab, store the block address in region[6], the seed size in block[6] (endow reads it back as the arena size), the parent libdir in block[64], the thread-exit sentinel in block[80], and the per-worker budget guard (g_worker_arena_budget, default 2 GiB) in block[82] (endow reads it as g_arena_budget). The worker grows from the seed up to the budget, pulling pool chunks on demand (fixed=0). Slice 4: propagates the kernel-pool anchor (g_kernel_pool_base@664, g_kernel_pool_end@672) and worker config (g_worker_arena_bytes@680, g_worker_arena_budget@688) into the child block, so the child's FS-relative pool globals are armed on load (the child's own loaded image starts with zero datums; this is what actually reaches launched workers).","module_name":"provision-worker-arena-block-into-region","package_name":"provision-worker-arena-block-into-region","function_definitions":{"provision-worker-arena-block-into-region":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"region","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"six","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":6},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"block_size","name":"g_worker_arena_bytes"},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"worker_budget","name":"g_worker_arena_budget"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"grab-released-or-fresh-arena-chunk","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"block_size"}],"result_assignment_variable":"arena_block","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"region","index":"six","value":"arena_block","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"arena_block","index":"six","value":"block_size","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"slot_libdir","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":64},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"parent_libdir","name":"g_ld_libdir"},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"arena_block","index":"slot_libdir","value":"parent_libdir","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"slot_exit","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":80},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"sentinel","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"arena_block","index":"slot_exit","value":"sentinel","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"idx656","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":82},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"arena_block","index":"idx656","value":"worker_budget","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"anc_base","name":"g_kernel_pool_base"},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"anc_end","name":"g_kernel_pool_end"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i83","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":83},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i84","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":84},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i85","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":85},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i86","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":86},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"arena_block","index":"i83","value":"anc_base","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"arena_block","index":"i84","value":"anc_end","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"arena_block","index":"i85","value":"block_size","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"arena_block","index":"i86","value":"worker_budget","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"arena_block"}}]}}}